PN,43901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FA teenage boy who lost seven litres of
OL,7,Fblood has called for more people to
OL,8,Fdonate the blood type which saved his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FElliott Wills, from Cornwall, was
OL,12,Fbleeding faster than donated blood
OL,13,Fcould be transfused into his body
OL,14,Fafter a main artery burst last year.
OL,16,FThe 13-year-old spent three weeks in
OL,17,Fhospital, but is now back playing
OL,18,Ffootball with his friends and
OL,19,Fpreparing to celebrate his birthday at
OL,20,Fthe end of the month.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
