OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FElliot has a disorder known as
OL,7,Fspherocytosis, an inherited condition
OL,8,Fthat affects the red blood cells and
OL,9,Fcan cause severe anaemia.
OL,11,FHe has a rare blood type ` B negative
OL,12,F` and regularly has transfusions to
OL,13,Fkeep him well.
OL,15,FComplications from a virus led to
OL,16,FElliot having his spleen and gall
OL,17,Fbladder removed last October, and
OL,18,Fwhile the procedure went well, a main
OL,19,Fartery burst afterwards and his family
OL,20,Fwere told to prepare for the worst.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FThe teenager was bleeding donated
OL,7,Fblood as fast as it could be
OL,8,Ftransfused, and a team of 20 staff
OL,9,Fspent three hours trying to save him.
OL,11,FElliott was given 23 units of blood,
OL,12,Fthe equivalent of seven litres ` or
OL,13,Fthree times his body's circulatory
OL,14,Fvolume.
OL,16,FHe was saved by emergency supplies of
OL,17,FO negative blood, which can be given
OL,18,Fto anyone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FElliott's father Phill, 53, said: "The
OL,7,Fsurgeon said Elliott basically lost
OL,8,Fall his blood.
OL,10,F"It was a race against time to get the
OL,11,Fdonated blood into him. But he was
OL,12,Flosing that too."
OL,14,FElliot's mother Gill had been unable
OL,15,Fto travel to Bristol Royal Hospital
OL,16,Ffor Children while Elliott was being
OL,17,Ftreated due to health reasons, and was
OL,18,Fat home in Truro with his 12-year-old
OL,19,Fsister Marnie.
OL,26,@nD@cOUrD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FMr Wills said: "When Elliott's notes
OL,7,Fsaid he'd lost seven litres I thought
OL,8,Fit was a typo.
OL,10,F"Surely no-one can survive losing that
OL,11,Fmuch blood? But Elliott is living
OL,12,Fproof they can, as long as the vital
OL,13,Fsupplies of donated blood are there."
OL,15,FAccording to NHS Blood and Transplant,
OL,16,Fthe number of regular donors with O
OL,17,Fnegative and B negative blood has
OL,18,Fdropped 5% since 2020.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FAround 107,000 donors with O negative
OL,7,Fblood do so regularly, some 6,000
OL,8,Ffewer than six years ago.
OL,10,FElliot spent three days in an induced
OL,11,Fcoma after his transfusions and three
OL,12,Fweeks recovering in hospital.
OL,14,FHe is now back at school and playing
OL,15,Ffootball with his friends again.
OL,17,FHe said: "Thank-you to everyone who
OL,18,Fgives blood. It helped saved my life.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,F"If you are thinking of giving blood,
OL,7,Fplease do. My mummy Gill had major
OL,8,Fspinal surgery back in March and also
OL,9,Fneeded lots of blood. I'm looking
OL,10,Fforward to my 14th birthday on June
OL,11,F29, a birthday I didn't think I would
OL,12,Fhave.
OL,14,F"Thank-you blood donors for my gift of
OL,15,Flife."
OL,17,FMr Wills added: "Elliott is kicking a
OL,18,Fball about again and that is because
OL,19,Fblood donors gave him a second chance
OL,20,Fat life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@FO]yD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,F"While Elliott was packing his
OL,7,Fhospital bag, someone out there was
OL,8,Fdonating the blood that would save his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"Donors are heroes and so are the NHS
OL,12,Fteams who get the blood from the
OL,13,Fdonor's arm into the veins of a
OL,14,Fdesperately ill patient like Elliott."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,FGerry Gogarty, director of blood
OL,7,Fsupply for NHS Blood and Transplant,
OL,8,Fsaid: "For Elliott, blood donations
OL,9,Fnot only ensured he survived a life-
OL,10,Fthreatening bleed, but also helped him
OL,11,Fto manage the blood disorder he lives
OL,12,Fwith.
OL,14,F"His experiences shine a light on just
OL,15,Fsome of the many ways that donors save
OL,16,Fand improve lives every day.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781097082
OL,3,CBoy from Cornwall who lost seven
OL,4,Clitres of blood pleads for more donors
OL,6,F"The NHS needs more people to give
OL,7,Fblood to help people like Elliott. All
OL,8,Fdonations are vital but new donors
OL,9,Fwith O negative, B negative and Ro
OL,10,Fblood are especially needed.
OL,12,F"You don't need to know your blood
OL,13,Ftype as you will find out after your
OL,14,Ffirst donation. Please register today
OL,15,Fand book an appointment. You may
OL,16,Fdiscover you have one of the 'missing
OL,17,Ftypes' that patients need right now."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
